{"tid":2405339,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴觀察難證無誤  救人阻差案 中六生脫罪","createTime":"2021-02-12T09:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T09:38:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa93c149be6e8747e2fb9fc56adf149fecf54db0","tid":2405339,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/GWMNUMKOMJFW5D3JF2U7KNCXFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210212%2FGWMNUMKOMJFW5D3JF2U7KNCXFI%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FLidffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=e934f3fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210212%2FGWMNUMKOMJFW5D3JF2U7KNCXFI%2F&h=dcc94b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/GWMNUMKOMJFW5D3JF2U7KNCXFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n防暴觀察難證無誤 <br />\n救人阻差案 中六生脫罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VDr7SoJWFykoJgG1WdlIFjC8DOM=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RHQRZ6UWVRGK3H4JB4NYSX27CA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVDr7SoJWFykoJgG1WdlIFjC8DOM%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRHQRZ6UWVRGK3H4JB4NYSX27CA.jpg&h=f3ac1cfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■報稱受阻的警員李文軒承認回頭察看時，攬他的人已轉身跑走，只看到其側臉。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】市民紀念元朗7.21襲擊事件八個月當晚，中六男生稱放工時遇上大批警員衝出來，決定掉頭走，卻被指出手拯救兩名遭防暴警追捕的女子，被控阻差辦公。案件昨裁決，裁判官梁雅忻指警員證供質素未能讓法庭確定他觀察無誤，辯方說法亦沒有不合情理之處，基於疑點利益歸於被告，裁定男生罪名不成立，<span class=\"orange\">庭上聞判掌聲雷動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n被告。。。。。。。。。。。被告。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官梁雅忻昨裁決時指，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「被攬到擰轉頭究竟隔幾耐」<br />\n<br />\n被告早前自辯稱，本打算到同事寓所休息，沿路看見有示威者與警員對峙，再目睹一名女子被制服，直至看見大批警員衝出，感不安而原路折返，隨即被撲出警員拘捕。梁官認為，被告與同事證供在盤問下「站得住腳」，而警員的證供質素，則未能讓她肯定其觀察無誤，基於疑點利益歸於被告，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC1848/20<br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">庭上聞判掌聲雷動</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有時間嘅要上庭聲援呀"},{"pid":"3bcc2a2efaaf28e8767bf08c2c0ab6e8b1a68b94","tid":2405339,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa12e0ca705cd04481b4417a96e8e54e5ea7a64c","tid":2405339,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">庭上聞判掌聲雷動</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有時間嘅要上庭聲援呀"},{"pid":"df7002fa85f99a803111ebcc592824e94ac2735a","tid":2405339,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa12e0ca705cd04481b4417a96e8e54e5ea7a64c","tid":2405339,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">庭上聞判掌聲雷動</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有時間嘅要上庭聲援呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:38:06.000Z","msg":"他日被濫捕濫告的可能是我也是你"}],"pinned":{"pid":"aa12e0ca705cd04481b4417a96e8e54e5ea7a64c","tid":2405339,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">庭上聞判掌聲雷動</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\